title: Interstellar / Galaxy voting / #2 / UNI $UNI
body:
First, we vote for the existing projects. The community decides whether to leave or remove them.

Then, if 1 or more slots from the available 9 becomes vacant, the community decides which project(s) from Galaxy will fill the vacancy / vacancies.
